1.0.name: wordpress/rt-prettyphoto
1.0.description:
This plugin will automatic add lightbox in wordpress post/page without disturbance.

Features

  • Easy to use.
  • Support Images, Youtube Video, Vimeo video, iFrame, DEV.
  • For image not need to add rel

Browser support

  • Firefox 3.0+ Google
  • Chrome 10.0+
  • Internet Explorer 6.0+
  • Safari 3.1.1+
  • Opera 9+

More

  • Thank you for using our plugin.
  • Vist the blog post to know more.
  • Give a Rating & Write a Review
